    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly impeccable, mint condition and presents exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. Every aspect of the car has been preserved with the utmost care, resulting in a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in pristine, original state. Mechanically, the vehicle is perfect, with all systems functioning exactly as designed and showing no signs of wear. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. Buyers can expect a vehicle that requires absolutely nothing but a new owner who appreciates perfection.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
