      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. The engine starts easily and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides reliable shifting across all gears. While the exterior paint retains a nice luster, you may find some minor cosmetic imperfections like small stone chips or light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. The interior is clean and comfortable, with all major electronics and climate control systems functioning as they should. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a solid, road-ready vehicle that has many miles of life left in it.",
      "price": 35500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
