      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Lexus RX 350 in Nebula Gray Pearl with a Parchment leather interior. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and remains in solid mechanical and aesthetic shape. The exterior paint retains a high gloss, though there are a few minor stone chips on the leading edge of the hood and a small 2-inch scuff on the lower rear plastic valence\u2014nothing that detracts from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin is a non-smoker environment; the leather seats are supple with no rips or thinning, though the driver's side bolster shows light entry wear. All technological features, including the 12.3-inch navigation display, heated/ventilated seats, and the power moonroof, function perfectly. Mechanically, this Lexus is sound with a complete service history from the local dealership; the 3.5L V6 runs smoothly and the 8-speed transmission shifts without hesitation. The tires have approximately 60% tread remaining, and the brakes were serviced just 4,000 miles ago. Included are two sets of keys, the original owner's manuals, and all-weather floor mats. This is a dependable, well-cared-for luxury SUV ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
